说一下 NSNotification 的实现机制？
发消息是同步还是异步？
NSNotification是同步进行的，一般情况下我们会在主线程发送通知在主线程接收通知，但是如果在接收消息中耗时较长会出现什么情况？
- (void)mainTheadNotification {
    NSLog(@"主线程开始current thread = %@", [NSThread currentThread]);
    NSString *str = @"mainTheadNotification";
    [[NSNotificationCenter defaultCenter] addObserver:self selector:@selector(handleNotification:) name:str object:nil];
    [[NSNotificationCenter defaultCenter] postNotificationName:str object:nil userInfo:nil];

    NSLog(@"主线程结束current thread = %@", [NSThread currentThread]);
}

//主线程接收消息
- (void)handleNotification:(NSNotification *)info {
    NSLog(@"模拟耗时操作");
    [NSThread sleepForTimeInterval:5.0f];
    NSLog(@"耗时操作结束");
}

打印结果如下
2020-05-01 15:29:06.264300+0800 NSNotification[2500:88784] 主线程开始current thread = {number = 1, name = main}
2020-05-01 15:29:06.264502+0800 NSNotification[2500:88784] 模拟耗时操作
2020-05-01 15:29:11.265390+0800 NSNotification[2500:88784] 耗时操作结束
2020-05-01 15:29:11.265716+0800 NSNotification[2500:88784] 主线程结束current thread = {number = 1, name = main}

这是由于NSNotification的同步性。即如果你在程序中的A位置post了一个NSNotification，在B位置注册了一个observer，通知发出后，必须等到B位置的通知回调执行完以后才能返回到A处继续往下执行。
NSNotification通知转发线程
那么如果在子线程发送消息会在哪里接收消息？
- (void)otherTheadNotification {

    NSString *str = @"otherTheadNotification";

    [[NSNotificationCenter defaultCenter] addObserver:self selector:@selector(handleNotification1:) name:str object:nil];

    dispatch_async(dispatch_get_global_queue(DISPATCH_QUEUE_PRIORITY_DEFAULT, 0), ^{
        NSLog(@"子线程开始current thread = %@", [NSThread currentThread]);

        [[NSNotificationCenter defaultCenter] postNotificationName:str object:nil userInfo:nil];
        NSLog(@"子线程结束current thread = %@", [NSThread currentThread]);
    });
}

//主线程接收消息
- (void)handleNotification1:(NSNotification *)info {
    NSLog(@"子线程模拟耗时操作--%@",[NSThread currentThread]);
    [NSThread sleepForTimeInterval:5.0f];
    NSLog(@"子线程耗时操作结束--%@",[NSThread currentThread]);

    //如果需要在主线程UI操作或其他操作
    dispatch_sync(dispatch_get_main_queue(), ^{
        NSLog(@"切换到主线程耗时操作结束--%@",[NSThread currentThread]);
    });
}

